      <title>德国商业银行任命首席财务官奥洛普为首席执行官，裕信银行增持股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/commerzbank-appoints-bettina-orlopp-ceo-unicredit-builds-up-stake-2024-09-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行周二宣布，贝蒂娜·奥洛普将在不久的将来接任该银行首席执行官，这使她成为德国第二大银行动荡时期最受瞩目的银行家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/commerzbank-appoints-bettina-orlopp-ceo-unicredit-builds-up-stake-2024-09-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国央行行长纳格尔称德国经济将复苏但仍需改革</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-economy-will-recover-still-needs-reforms-bundesbanks-nagel-says-2024-09-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长约阿希姆纳格尔周三表示，随着高通胀和利率等暂时不利因素消退，德国经济将会复苏，但该国仍然需要从移民到儿童保育等重大改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-economy-will-recover-still-needs-reforms-bundesbanks-nagel-says-2024-09-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 16:08:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
